<META NAME="SUMMARY" CONTENT="Federal Medical Marijuana Attracts Bi-Partisan Support First Two Republicans Sign On To Bill...Funding For Study On Medical Marijuana Allocated In Washington State Budget...Domestic Hemp Cultivation Bill Heads To Colorado Senate...Washington State Medical Marijuana User Found Guilty Of Drug Possession And Manufacture Charges...Rally For Medical Marijuana To Be Held This Saturday...">
<META NAME="keywords" CONTENT="NORML, Marijuana, marijuana, Cannabis, cannabis, Hemp, hemp">
