<meta name="author" content="NORML">
<meta name="date" content="March 9, 1995">
<meta name="SUMMARY"
content="Editor of Arkansas Times Comes out of Her 'Smoky Little Closet'...Alleged white House Shootist Reportedly Smoked Pot and Listened to Rush Limbaugh.&nbsp;  A Dangerous Combination?...New Test Allows Parents to Test Their Children's Rooms for 'Drugs'...Marijuana Plants Thrive In Downtown Tel Aviv.&nbsp;  Is Marijuana Decriminalization Coming To Isreal?...REMINDER: ABC News Special To Focus On The 'War On Drugs'...">
