65 ?   Sumskaya           580    180    80 
<b>120</b>    <b>Transcarp.</b> <b>Reg.</b>  <b>1,250</b>    <b>147</b> <b>1,000</b> 
127    Transcarp. Reg.    570    150 1,045 
<b>132</b>    <b>Transcarp.</b> <b>Reg.</b>  <b>1,000</b>    <b>145</b>   <b>990</b> 
