<DOCHDR>
http://206.61.184.43:80/schaffer/lsd/ute.htm 206.61.184.43 19970122063710 text/html 18379
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 06:37:00 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N wpo-0deb)
